{
  "text": "The measured rate of oxygen consumption for B. subtilis is in the range of 0.5-2 \u00d7 10 6 molecules s \u22121 cell \u22121 [CITATION_1] . Oxygen concentration at the airsuspension interface is less than 10 mg l \u22121 \u00aa 10 5 molecules mm \u22123",
